data.description: Welcome to your cozy country home in Santa Fe! This adorable move-in ready 2 bedroom, 1 bath home sits on a quiet, peaceful 1 acre lot. Mature trees dot the landscape and the huge backyard is a great spot for a pool, playground, shop or all 3! The sky’s the limit! You’ll also find a shed that stays with the property as well as a 2 car carport, providing covered parking during those stormy days. As you enter the home, you’ll discover a large living room with big windows and lots of natural light. You’ll also find a kitchen with breakfast bar and a cozy eat-in dining space. Two large bedrooms and a full bath are located in the back of the home. Located close to restaurants, shopping, main roads and more! Zoned for Santa Fe ISD! Do not miss this one! Schedule your private showing today!
